# Pre-commit checks

This repo has tests (unit + CLI). Before committing, ensure formatting, build, lint, and tests pass locally:

- `gofmt -w -s .`
- `make build`
- `make lint`
- `make test`

If you are using the task runner directly, the equivalents are:

- `./.tool/task format`
- `./.tool/task build`
- `./.tool/task lint`
- `./.tool/task test`
